1
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:40,980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

2
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,990
=Episode 34=

3
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:50,180
Commandant Wu,

4
00:01:50,830 --> 00:01:51,700
how is your injury?

5
00:01:52,860 --> 00:01:53,700
General,

6
00:01:54,390 --> 00:01:55,700
sorry I let you down.

7
00:02:01,630 --> 00:02:02,550
I've heard about it.

8
00:02:03,190 --> 00:02:04,470
What exactly happened there?

9
00:02:05,630 --> 00:02:06,470
At that time,

10
00:02:06,830 --> 00:02:07,750
Captain Meng and I

11
00:02:07,750 --> 00:02:09,140
were raiding their main forces

12
00:02:09,140 --> 00:02:10,700
according to your splitting strategy

13
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:12,070
when we were nearly ambushed.

14
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:14,390
Those Chong soldiers who attacked us

15
00:02:15,230 --> 00:02:16,070
were very weird.

16
00:02:16,830 --> 00:02:17,670
They seemed

17
00:02:18,270 --> 00:02:19,110
fearless of pain.

18
00:02:19,860 --> 00:02:20,700
What's worse,

19
00:02:20,990 --> 00:02:22,070
when we retreated,

20
00:02:22,070 --> 00:02:23,350
many enemy assassins

21
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:24,230
suddenly appeared

22
00:02:24,230 --> 00:02:25,790
out of nowhere.

23
00:02:26,230 --> 00:02:27,990
We were caught

24
00:02:27,990 --> 00:02:29,790
completely off guard.

25
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:36,420
The All-Knowing was there.

26
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:38,860
What was our loss?

27
00:02:40,350 --> 00:02:41,900
By the time I realized the problem,

28
00:02:42,420 --> 00:02:44,110
we had lost 40 percent of our forces.

29
00:02:44,390 --> 00:02:45,700
I didn't dare to get bogged down,

30
00:02:46,140 --> 00:02:47,950
so I led our troops in retreat.

31
00:02:48,390 --> 00:02:49,230
Commandant Wu,

32
00:02:49,990 --> 00:02:51,300
the battlefield is unpredictable.

33
00:02:51,830 --> 00:02:52,790
You did well enough.

34
00:02:53,830 --> 00:02:54,670
I'll send scouts

35
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:56,070
to find out what happened.

36
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:29,420
When I offered you presents,

37
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:32,230
you'd at least give them a good look.

38
00:03:35,830 --> 00:03:36,830
Now when I think of it,

39
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:38,390
these common things

40
00:03:39,180 --> 00:03:40,550
really don't suit you.

41
00:04:01,110 --> 00:04:01,950
I've made you

42
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:03,350
a queen's crown by myself.

43
00:04:05,300 --> 00:04:06,230
Won't you try it on?

44
00:04:07,350 --> 00:04:09,020
The one who wanted this crown

45
00:04:09,020 --> 00:04:10,900
was killed by you.

46
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:15,180
Yan Zhang trained those puppet spirits

47
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:17,470
for you, didn't she?

48
00:04:20,470 --> 00:04:22,060
She was completely devoted to you.

49
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:24,500
When you killed her,

50
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:26,230
you didn't even bat an eye.

51
00:04:28,380 --> 00:04:29,710
You've found out.

52
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:33,820
My queen's crown

53
00:04:34,550 --> 00:04:36,110
will only be yours.

54
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:39,790
You so-called love

55
00:04:41,670 --> 00:04:43,060
makes me sick.

56
00:04:45,230 --> 00:04:46,670
Here it is again, the same old look.

57
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:49,780
Simu,

58
00:04:50,860 --> 00:04:52,230
the first time I saw you,

59
00:04:53,060 --> 00:04:54,260
I fell in love

60
00:04:54,590 --> 00:04:56,500
with your disdainful look.

61
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:58,230
From then on,

62
00:04:58,790 --> 00:05:00,380
I could hardly forget that.

63
00:05:02,590 --> 00:05:04,180
But I don't like it

64
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:05,990
when you look at me

65
00:05:05,990 --> 00:05:08,260
as if I were an ant!

66
00:05:31,860 --> 00:05:33,300
It fits you perfectly,

67
00:05:33,910 --> 00:05:34,940
my queen.

68
00:06:14,990 --> 00:06:15,830
Simu,

69
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:19,300
I've spoiled you too much.

70
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:24,260
Get out of here.

71
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,140
I will

72
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:07,740
have these things replaced.

73
00:07:09,590 --> 00:07:10,820
No matter how many you crush,

74
00:07:11,420 --> 00:07:12,550
I'll just have them replaced.

75
00:07:15,470 --> 00:07:16,310
No need.

76
00:07:18,350 --> 00:07:19,790
I don't like dead things.

77
00:08:45,310 --> 00:08:46,540
Why is His Lordship up there?

78
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:47,500
Isn't it inappropriate?

79
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:50,290
During Her Grace's seclusion,

80
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:52,020
for the sake of convenience,

81
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:53,340
from this day on,

82
00:08:53,830 --> 00:08:55,740
I'll be the acting sovereign.

83
00:08:56,140 --> 00:08:57,710
All of you shall obey my orders

84
00:08:57,990 --> 00:08:59,020
without fail.

85
00:09:00,540 --> 00:09:01,990
Does this come from Her Grace?

86
00:09:02,830 --> 00:09:03,710
Yes, Your Lordship.

87
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:04,860
You...

88
00:09:05,740 --> 00:09:07,110
Yes, Your Lordship.

89
00:09:08,110 --> 00:09:10,110
Yes, Your Lordship.

90
00:09:14,950 --> 00:09:15,790
Your Lordship,

91
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:17,990
the 24 Temples and the Ascension Pool

92
00:09:17,990 --> 00:09:19,020
have been searched.

93
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:20,660
Jiang Ai hasn't been found.

94
00:09:21,350 --> 00:09:22,430
I've sent my men

95
00:09:22,620 --> 00:09:23,990
to search all the valleys.

96
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:25,710
I believe we'll find her soon.

97
00:09:50,110 --> 00:09:50,990
You may leave too.

98
00:09:52,110 --> 00:09:53,500
Do I have the honor

99
00:09:54,110 --> 00:09:55,620
to ease your worries,

100
00:09:55,620 --> 00:09:56,460
Your Lordship?

101
00:10:03,740 --> 00:10:05,230
What do you think

102
00:10:06,070 --> 00:10:07,310
is a dead thing

103
00:10:08,140 --> 00:10:09,620
and what is a living thing?

104
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:13,110
In my opinion,

105
00:10:14,710 --> 00:10:15,900
dead things are in the Void.

106
00:10:16,470 --> 00:10:17,310
Living things are

107
00:10:18,070 --> 00:10:18,990
in the Mortal World.

108
00:10:21,740 --> 00:10:23,070
This cup is originally

109
00:10:23,070 --> 00:10:24,310
from the Mortal World.

110
00:10:25,620 --> 00:10:27,260
Then why is it a dead thing

111
00:10:27,950 --> 00:10:29,540
in our world?

112
00:10:32,260 --> 00:10:33,230
Perhaps because

113
00:10:33,590 --> 00:10:35,110
it was never meant to belong here.

114
00:10:53,310 --> 00:10:54,310
Flowers for sale.

115
00:10:56,110 --> 00:10:56,990
Flowers.

116
00:10:58,860 --> 00:10:59,740
Flowers for sale.

117
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:02,590
Flowers for sale.

118
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:06,020
Miss, would you like some flowers?

119
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:07,310
No, thank you.

120
00:11:09,350 --> 00:11:11,430
- Living things?
- Flowers.

121
00:11:41,830 --> 00:11:43,500
(The Void is a dead land.)

122
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:45,140
(Earthly things)

123
00:11:45,140 --> 00:11:47,020
(can't survive here.)

124
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:50,110
(But I'll force them.)

125
00:14:08,430 --> 00:14:09,270
It's done.

126
00:14:11,190 --> 00:14:12,110
Xu,

127
00:14:12,110 --> 00:14:13,070
get some rest early.

128
00:14:15,140 --> 00:14:15,980
I'm all right now.

129
00:14:17,110 --> 00:14:17,950
You should go to bed.

130
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:19,610
- But...
- I'm fine now.

131
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:40,700
(Back in Weizhou,)

132
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:42,990
(we suffered heavy losses.)

133
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:45,620
(I must make)

134
00:14:45,620 --> 00:14:46,460
(a new strategy)

135
00:14:47,380 --> 00:14:48,230
(to retake Weizhou)

136
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:51,110
(and avenge our dead soldiers.)

137
00:14:55,070 --> 00:14:56,590
Chenying was right.

138
00:14:57,740 --> 00:14:58,860
Great Ancestor wouldn't want

139
00:14:58,860 --> 00:14:59,700
to see you like this.

140
00:15:07,890 --> 00:15:08,740
Luda has become

141
00:15:08,740 --> 00:15:09,710
the High Priest.

142
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:13,190
I don't know how,

143
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:14,710
but he made his army

144
00:15:14,710 --> 00:15:15,780
fearless of death.

145
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:18,660
We're at a stalemate

146
00:15:18,660 --> 00:15:19,500
with them.

147
00:15:20,830 --> 00:15:22,110
My injury is no big deal.

148
00:15:23,620 --> 00:15:24,990
I examined the enemy's blood

149
00:15:25,230 --> 00:15:27,020
on Commandant Xia's weapon.

150
00:15:27,710 --> 00:15:29,110
I found out they were poisoned.

151
00:15:29,830 --> 00:15:31,780
With this poison in their wounds,

152
00:15:32,070 --> 00:15:33,470
the soldiers won't feel the pain

153
00:15:34,070 --> 00:15:35,590
and they'll fight until death.

154
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:39,430
Luda used poison

155
00:15:39,430 --> 00:15:40,660
to manipulate his soldiers.

156
00:15:43,710 --> 00:15:45,710
What a great cost.

157
00:15:47,190 --> 00:15:48,030
To win this war,

158
00:15:48,900 --> 00:15:50,380
he has gone insane.

159
00:15:52,430 --> 00:15:54,110
We both have suffered losses.

160
00:15:54,380 --> 00:15:55,590
The war is deadlocked.

161
00:15:56,230 --> 00:15:57,380
Why don't you calm down

162
00:15:57,590 --> 00:15:58,430
and think carefully?

163
00:15:58,660 --> 00:15:59,950
Don't let panic take over,

164
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:01,190
or you'll take the bait.

165
00:16:02,230 --> 00:16:03,660
If Great Ancestor returns

166
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:05,620
and finds you dead,

167
00:16:06,230 --> 00:16:07,710
your future will be ruined.

168
00:16:07,860 --> 00:16:09,430
So will mine.

169
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:19,900
What's happening with Simu?

170
00:16:23,540 --> 00:16:24,830
Something must be wrong with her.

171
00:16:27,110 --> 00:16:28,260
Still won't tell the truth?

172
00:16:30,540 --> 00:16:31,380
The Void...

173
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:37,310
Something indeed happened there.

174
00:16:37,660 --> 00:16:38,620
But not very serious.

175
00:16:40,070 --> 00:16:41,430
If the Sovereign vanished,

176
00:16:41,950 --> 00:16:42,830
the Mortal World

177
00:16:42,830 --> 00:16:44,190
would definitely suffer.

178
00:16:44,620 --> 00:16:45,500
Great Ancestor

179
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:46,710
wouldn't allow such a thing

180
00:16:46,710 --> 00:16:47,550
to happen.

181
00:16:48,990 --> 00:16:49,860
General Duan,

182
00:16:51,070 --> 00:16:53,110
you must stay alive.

183
00:16:53,660 --> 00:16:55,190
Before she comes back to you,

184
00:16:56,110 --> 00:16:57,660
you have to be alive.

185
00:17:04,630 --> 00:17:05,910
I must stay alive too.

186
00:17:07,060 --> 00:17:07,900
Let's go.

187
00:17:22,990 --> 00:17:23,830
(Simu,)

188
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:26,190
(I await your return.)

189
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:16,030
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

190
00:18:16,360 --> 00:18:20,610
♪Light encountered shadow♪

191
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:27,340
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

192
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:32,240
♪The unbreakable fate♪

193
00:18:33,330 --> 00:18:35,170
♪Suddenly cracked♪

194
00:18:47,420 --> 00:18:52,750
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

195
00:18:53,080 --> 00:18:57,330
♪Light encountered shadow♪

196
00:18:58,690 --> 00:19:04,060
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

197
00:19:04,360 --> 00:19:08,460
♪The unbreakable fate♪

198
00:19:08,460 --> 00:19:09,780
(Xiazhou)

199
00:19:09,780 --> 00:19:10,670
(Five years later,)

200
00:19:11,430 --> 00:19:13,060
(Duan Xu led the Liang Army)

201
00:19:13,390 --> 00:19:17,470
(to conquer Yingzhou, Tanzhou,
Ruzhou, and Mozhou.)

202
00:19:18,260 --> 00:19:21,060
(But heavy forces of the Chong Army)

203
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:22,990
(still besieged them menacingly.)

204
00:19:33,380 --> 00:19:37,020
(Young Xue Chenying)

205
00:19:39,100 --> 00:19:42,260
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

206
00:19:42,260 --> 00:19:44,790
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

207
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:50,310
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

208
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:53,550
♪Following fate's guidance♪

209
00:19:53,550 --> 00:19:58,410
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

210
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:01,770
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

211
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:08,360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

212
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:12,870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

213
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:19,630
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

214
00:20:19,860 --> 00:20:23,800
♪The unbreakable fate♪

215
00:20:25,570 --> 00:20:27,460
♪Suddenly cracked♪

216
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:33,280
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

217
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:35,810
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

218
00:20:35,810 --> 00:20:41,330
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

219
00:20:41,330 --> 00:20:44,570
♪Following fate's guidance♪

220
00:20:44,570 --> 00:20:49,430
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

221
00:20:49,770 --> 00:20:52,790
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

222
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:55,610
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

223
00:20:55,870 --> 00:20:58,400
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

224
00:20:58,400 --> 00:21:03,820
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

225
00:21:03,990 --> 00:21:07,060
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

226
00:21:07,220 --> 00:21:12,120
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

227
00:21:12,330 --> 00:21:15,800
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

228
00:21:45,990 --> 00:21:46,990
It's almost time.

229
00:22:11,260 --> 00:22:12,100
Don't give me that look.

230
00:22:13,100 --> 00:22:14,100
I don't do this for you,

231
00:22:14,630 --> 00:22:15,630
but for Simu.

232
00:22:17,150 --> 00:22:18,100
Get better quickly.

233
00:22:21,870 --> 00:22:22,820
I've wanted to ask.

234
00:22:23,300 --> 00:22:24,260
Everyone in the Void

235
00:22:24,260 --> 00:22:25,470
wants to be the Sovereign.

236
00:22:26,630 --> 00:22:27,820
Why did you

237
00:22:28,990 --> 00:22:30,260
submit to He Simu?

238
00:22:37,430 --> 00:22:39,500
In the past 300 years under her reign,

239
00:22:40,430 --> 00:22:41,470
the Void has been the best

240
00:22:41,470 --> 00:22:42,670
I've ever seen.

241
00:22:43,580 --> 00:22:45,870
No one else can be a better sovereign.

242
00:22:51,540 --> 00:22:52,740
Since you told me

243
00:22:52,910 --> 00:22:54,150
what happened during her reign,

244
00:22:54,670 --> 00:22:55,630
I've been thinking.

245
00:22:56,740 --> 00:22:57,630
If I had managed

246
00:22:57,630 --> 00:22:58,670
to be the Sovereign,

247
00:22:59,340 --> 00:23:00,580
the Void under my reign...

248
00:23:02,990 --> 00:23:03,830
It might be

249
00:23:03,990 --> 00:23:05,300
as terrible as it is now.

250
00:23:10,870 --> 00:23:11,870
The real sovereign should

251
00:23:12,630 --> 00:23:13,540
go back to the throne.

252
00:23:15,500 --> 00:23:17,020
Any news on the Left Token?

253
00:23:17,740 --> 00:23:18,740
Haven't found it yet.

254
00:23:21,190 --> 00:23:23,580
What about Jiang Ai and Bai Sanxing?

255
00:23:24,100 --> 00:23:24,940
Still searching.

256
00:23:25,780 --> 00:23:26,670
It's been five years.

257
00:23:27,190 --> 00:23:28,780
You haven't even found two spirits!

258
00:23:30,820 --> 00:23:31,660
Your Lordship,

259
00:23:31,950 --> 00:23:32,820
as long as Jiang Ai

260
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:33,780
still holds the Token,

261
00:23:34,430 --> 00:23:35,300
we can't open

262
00:23:35,300 --> 00:23:36,430
the spirit stone storehouse

263
00:23:36,870 --> 00:23:37,910
to get any stones out.

264
00:23:38,870 --> 00:23:40,230
She's been hiding for five years.

265
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:41,580
Our spirit stones

266
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:42,870
are almost used up.

267
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:44,340
And yesterday,

268
00:23:44,340 --> 00:23:45,710
a large number of spirits gathered.

269
00:23:46,190 --> 00:23:47,300
They attacked the 24 Temples

270
00:23:47,300 --> 00:23:48,140
and ransacked them.

271
00:23:49,260 --> 00:23:50,100
Luckily, I led my men

272
00:23:50,670 --> 00:23:51,510
to execute them.

273
00:23:53,470 --> 00:23:54,670
Outside the Sovereign's Hall,

274
00:23:54,990 --> 00:23:56,190
chaos has been everywhere.

275
00:23:56,820 --> 00:23:57,660
That's right.

276
00:24:15,740 --> 00:24:16,580
Your Lordship,

277
00:24:16,780 --> 00:24:17,780
we located Jiang Ai.

278
00:24:26,740 --> 00:24:28,980
(Ascension Pool)

279
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:41,430
Yan Ke,

280
00:24:42,390 --> 00:24:43,540
since you're here,

281
00:24:44,100 --> 00:24:45,390
why don't you come out?

282
00:24:49,950 --> 00:24:51,150
Give me the Left Token

283
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:53,500
and I'll let you leave the Void.

284
00:24:55,100 --> 00:24:56,820
I don't want to be hunted down

285
00:24:57,190 --> 00:24:59,340
by the Starhaven Sect
in the Mortal World.

286
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:00,820
Then you stay here

287
00:25:00,820 --> 00:25:01,950
and get annihilated!

288
00:25:17,150 --> 00:25:17,990
Yan Ke,

289
00:25:18,500 --> 00:25:19,910
how dare you appear before me?

290
00:25:22,580 --> 00:25:24,430
Does Simu know you brought out

291
00:25:25,820 --> 00:25:26,870
your old lover?

292
00:25:27,820 --> 00:25:29,670
Let me ask you this.

293
00:25:30,500 --> 00:25:32,780
If Simu finds out

294
00:25:32,780 --> 00:25:34,670
you killed her father,

295
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:36,820
what will you do?

296
00:25:39,390 --> 00:25:40,230
What...

297
00:25:52,670 --> 00:25:54,580
You even killed your own kind.

298
00:25:55,100 --> 00:25:56,430
You're really merciless.

299
00:25:57,540 --> 00:25:58,580
It was you

300
00:25:58,580 --> 00:26:00,150
who killed He Simu's father.

301
00:26:00,580 --> 00:26:02,630
But you stayed by her side deceitfully

302
00:26:03,020 --> 00:26:04,060
and asked her to kill me,

303
00:26:04,060 --> 00:26:05,300
the only witness to the truth.

304
00:26:05,710 --> 00:26:07,150
If He Simu finds out,

305
00:26:09,670 --> 00:26:11,300
she'll tear you apart.

306
00:26:12,780 --> 00:26:14,910
That's why you were so nervous.

307
00:26:15,670 --> 00:26:16,540
So you weren't scared

308
00:26:16,540 --> 00:26:18,150
that Bai Sanxing would find you.

309
00:26:18,710 --> 00:26:20,150
You were scared

310
00:26:20,150 --> 00:26:21,870
that Her Grace would know the truth

311
00:26:22,020 --> 00:26:23,870
after she met with Bai Sanxing.

312
00:26:24,260 --> 00:26:25,990
You talk too much.

313
00:26:33,580 --> 00:26:34,740
300 years ago,

314
00:26:34,740 --> 00:26:36,190
I might have feared you.

315
00:26:36,630 --> 00:26:37,580
But being stuck in there

316
00:26:37,580 --> 00:26:38,710
for that long

317
00:26:39,260 --> 00:26:40,910
has left you far weaker than before.

318
00:27:02,670 --> 00:27:03,510
Leave.

319
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:12,700
(Left)

320
00:27:16,260 --> 00:27:17,950
You can't get away.

321
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:20,820
The whole Void

322
00:27:21,670 --> 00:27:24,060
will soon be mine.

323
00:27:59,260 --> 00:28:00,100
Simu,

324
00:28:01,100 --> 00:28:02,300
I suddenly remembered.

325
00:28:02,990 --> 00:28:03,870
Today is the day

326
00:28:03,870 --> 00:28:05,230
we first met 300 years ago.

327
00:28:05,950 --> 00:28:07,500
We should celebrate this anniversary.

328
00:28:11,430 --> 00:28:12,500
That day, as I remember,

329
00:28:12,990 --> 00:28:14,300
thousands of spirits rebelled.

330
00:28:14,820 --> 00:28:16,060
You held the Kunwu Blade

331
00:28:16,430 --> 00:28:18,260
to suppress them alone.

332
00:28:19,630 --> 00:28:21,060
That was the first time I saw you.

333
00:28:22,260 --> 00:28:23,740
You were shining brilliantly.

334
00:28:25,230 --> 00:28:26,070
Simu,

335
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:28,230
you always say

336
00:28:28,230 --> 00:28:29,820
I want supreme power.

337
00:28:30,910 --> 00:28:31,750
You are wrong.

338
00:28:32,390 --> 00:28:33,470
I want both,

339
00:28:34,630 --> 00:28:35,470
you and power.

340
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:39,340
Without you, I couldn't

341
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:40,430
govern the Void well.

342
00:28:40,910 --> 00:28:41,750
Without you,

343
00:28:43,950 --> 00:28:45,710
everything would be meaningless.

344
00:28:57,670 --> 00:28:58,670
Today really is a day

345
00:28:58,670 --> 00:28:59,990
worth celebrating.

346
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:02,300
300 years ago,

347
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:03,670
my father suddenly died.

348
00:29:05,190 --> 00:29:06,150
I had no choice

349
00:29:07,260 --> 00:29:08,500
but to take over the Void.

350
00:29:15,870 --> 00:29:16,820
And today,

351
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:21,580
I'll kill the one
who murdered my father.

352
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:41,950
You... You know that?

353
00:29:44,260 --> 00:29:46,060
I heard what you said

354
00:29:46,950 --> 00:29:48,340
on the Void Mountain.

355
00:30:08,100 --> 00:30:09,630
I've done a lot of things these years.

356
00:30:09,630 --> 00:30:11,060
This is the only thing

357
00:30:11,870 --> 00:30:13,300
I never want you to know.

358
00:30:14,950 --> 00:30:16,820
Back then, I wanted to be the Sovereign.

359
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:18,190
So I had no choice

360
00:30:18,190 --> 00:30:19,740
but to kill him.

361
00:30:21,260 --> 00:30:22,500
But for your sake,

362
00:30:23,300 --> 00:30:24,300
I've been the Right Hand

363
00:30:24,300 --> 00:30:25,580
over the past 300 years

364
00:30:25,580 --> 00:30:27,020
and never complained!

365
00:30:29,190 --> 00:30:31,150
Yet you still don't accept me.

366
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:34,580
So I have to lock you here.

367
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:40,190
But all these things

368
00:30:40,190 --> 00:30:41,470
no longer matter.

369
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:43,380
Simu,

370
00:30:44,500 --> 00:30:45,910
I'll make it up to you.

371
00:30:47,300 --> 00:30:48,580
You love the Mortal World, right?

372
00:30:49,260 --> 00:30:51,100
I wouldn't mind uniting

373
00:30:51,100 --> 00:30:52,100
the two worlds.

374
00:30:52,820 --> 00:30:54,150
Wherever you want to go,

375
00:30:54,430 --> 00:30:55,500
I'll go there with you.

376
00:30:57,060 --> 00:30:58,670
Just don't leave me.

377
00:31:02,870 --> 00:31:04,020
You killed my father.

378
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:08,740
Does it

379
00:31:08,740 --> 00:31:10,230
really matter that much?

380
00:31:12,190 --> 00:31:13,740
If I hadn't killed him,

381
00:31:14,500 --> 00:31:15,500
would things be different

382
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:16,780
between us?

383
00:31:18,820 --> 00:31:20,020
There's no if!

384
00:31:49,260 --> 00:31:50,300
This is where your father

385
00:31:50,300 --> 00:31:52,060
established the Golden-wall Decrees.

386
00:31:54,540 --> 00:31:56,100
You want to avenge him, don't you?

387
00:31:57,670 --> 00:31:59,260
Then let's end this

388
00:31:59,540 --> 00:32:00,630
right here and now.

389
00:33:30,150 --> 00:33:30,990
Stop the pursuit.

390
00:33:32,150 --> 00:33:33,230
That was my oversight.

391
00:33:34,740 --> 00:33:36,100
He pretended to fight me

392
00:33:36,540 --> 00:33:37,740
just to grab the Glazed Pagoda

393
00:33:38,260 --> 00:33:39,780
to hide his aura and make his escape.

394
00:33:40,990 --> 00:33:42,430
He's out of reach now.

395
00:34:19,100 --> 00:34:20,430
You were expelled from the Void?

396
00:34:28,540 --> 00:34:29,540
Who allowed you

397
00:34:29,540 --> 00:34:31,060
to talk to me like this?

398
00:34:33,620 --> 00:34:34,870
You came here

399
00:34:34,870 --> 00:34:36,020
to seek my help, didn't you?

400
00:34:37,270 --> 00:34:38,110
Help?

401
00:34:39,100 --> 00:34:40,020
You don't deserve it.

402
00:34:41,270 --> 00:34:42,430
In that case,

403
00:34:43,310 --> 00:34:44,350
I won't hold you back.

404
00:34:48,700 --> 00:34:50,700
You're merely a pawn.

405
00:34:51,660 --> 00:34:52,950
I can give you power,

406
00:34:53,270 --> 00:34:55,220
and I can take it back anytime.

407
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:57,700
You'd better get that straight.

408
00:34:59,060 --> 00:35:00,750
Don't think being the High Priest

409
00:35:01,100 --> 00:35:02,830
means you have nothing to worry about.

410
00:35:04,140 --> 00:35:06,180
If the North Chong falls,

411
00:35:06,700 --> 00:35:08,950
you'll perish with it too.

412
00:35:18,790 --> 00:35:20,700
Duan Xu never loses a battle

413
00:35:21,430 --> 00:35:23,750
simply because he has a pact
with the Sovereign.

414
00:35:24,950 --> 00:35:26,470
No wonder in Youzhou,

415
00:35:27,430 --> 00:35:29,790
his power was unmatched.

416
00:35:30,910 --> 00:35:31,750
That's right.

417
00:35:34,310 --> 00:35:36,020
The Sovereign is back on the throne.

418
00:35:36,910 --> 00:35:39,220
The course of the war will be affected.

419
00:35:43,220 --> 00:35:44,100
What should I do?

420
00:35:46,660 --> 00:35:47,660
When I'm around,

421
00:35:48,390 --> 00:35:49,950
you will succeed.

422
00:35:51,830 --> 00:35:54,470
All you have to do is follow my orders.

423
00:36:10,310 --> 00:36:11,270
Simu,

424
00:36:11,270 --> 00:36:12,430
you're finally back.

425
00:36:28,020 --> 00:36:28,860
Bai Sanxing,

426
00:36:30,790 --> 00:36:32,060
what are your plans for future?

427
00:36:33,430 --> 00:36:34,500
Will you still fight me

428
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,620
for the throne?

429
00:36:39,390 --> 00:36:40,230
It depends.

430
00:36:40,910 --> 00:36:41,870
300 years ago,

431
00:36:41,870 --> 00:36:42,910
I rose against He Yicheng.

432
00:36:43,470 --> 00:36:44,350
Then now,

433
00:36:46,180 --> 00:36:47,060
I could do the same.

434
00:36:49,580 --> 00:36:50,420
I'll be waiting.

435
00:36:51,220 --> 00:36:52,180
Feel free to try.

436
00:36:57,020 --> 00:36:57,860
Back then,

437
00:36:58,060 --> 00:36:59,500
I naively believed Yan Ke.

438
00:37:32,370 --> 00:37:33,220
I thought he meant

439
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:34,270
to help me,

440
00:37:34,500 --> 00:37:35,390
so he killed He Yicheng

441
00:37:35,950 --> 00:37:37,700
and spread rumors that he died for love.

442
00:37:38,990 --> 00:37:39,830
To my surprise,

443
00:37:40,180 --> 00:37:41,060
he then

444
00:37:41,470 --> 00:37:43,020
worked with you to trap me.

445
00:37:48,180 --> 00:37:49,580
Not until he and Jiang Ai

446
00:37:50,100 --> 00:37:51,350
lured me into the Prison

447
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:53,060
and the three of you attacked me

448
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:54,420
did I realize

449
00:37:54,950 --> 00:37:56,580
that everything was just his trap.

450
00:37:58,990 --> 00:37:59,830
Unfortunately,

451
00:38:00,950 --> 00:38:01,830
it was too late.

452
00:38:04,910 --> 00:38:05,950
I never believed

453
00:38:05,950 --> 00:38:06,990
my father died for love.

454
00:38:08,020 --> 00:38:09,500
You were arrogant and rebellious,

455
00:38:10,830 --> 00:38:12,220
but you never took advantage.

456
00:38:13,270 --> 00:38:14,470
If you had killed my father,

457
00:38:15,310 --> 00:38:16,830
you would have told everyone.

458
00:38:17,790 --> 00:38:20,390
You didn't need that excuse.

459
00:38:22,180 --> 00:38:23,140
I won't get over it

460
00:38:23,660 --> 00:38:25,270
until I capture Yan Ke.

461
00:38:28,390 --> 00:38:29,230
From this day,

462
00:38:31,580 --> 00:38:32,910
hunt down the traitor Yan Ke.

463
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:34,870
Restart the curfew.

464
00:38:35,580 --> 00:38:36,540
Thoroughly investigate

465
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:38,100
all riots over the past five years.

466
00:38:38,580 --> 00:38:39,910
Severely punish those who violated

467
00:38:41,180 --> 00:38:42,140
the Golden-wall Decrees.

468
00:38:43,990 --> 00:38:44,830
Yes.

469
00:38:48,990 --> 00:38:49,830
Move!

470
00:38:52,660 --> 00:38:54,100
Officer, I heard...

471
00:38:54,100 --> 00:38:55,350
Her Grace ended her seclusion

472
00:38:55,350 --> 00:38:56,390
and restarted the Decrees.

473
00:38:56,390 --> 00:38:57,390
Is that true, officer?

474
00:38:59,580 --> 00:39:00,830
Orders from Her Grace!

475
00:39:01,540 --> 00:39:02,660
Riots in the past five years

476
00:39:03,020 --> 00:39:04,180
will be investigated!

477
00:39:04,750 --> 00:39:06,100
- Excellent!
- Great!

478
00:39:06,100 --> 00:39:06,940
Move!

479
00:39:07,140 --> 00:39:07,980
This is great.

480
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:09,060
Her Grace is back.

481
00:39:09,910 --> 00:39:11,430
I'm finally safe.

482
00:39:11,430 --> 00:39:12,270
Great!

483
00:39:12,470 --> 00:39:13,910
Her Grace is back!

484
00:39:16,540 --> 00:39:17,580
Awesome!

485
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:21,910
The Left Token is back with me.

486
00:39:22,500 --> 00:39:23,910
The spirit stones have been

487
00:39:23,910 --> 00:39:24,870
orderly distributed.

488
00:39:26,540 --> 00:39:27,390
It's been five years.

489
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:28,700
I'm so happy to see you

490
00:39:28,990 --> 00:39:29,910
safe and sound.

491
00:39:31,310 --> 00:39:32,150
It's been five years.

492
00:39:32,580 --> 00:39:34,180
You're still as exuberant

493
00:39:34,310 --> 00:39:35,150
as before.

494
00:39:35,540 --> 00:39:36,990
How I envy you.

495
00:39:37,750 --> 00:39:39,100
You faithless traitor.

496
00:39:39,520 --> 00:39:40,390
For five years,

497
00:39:40,390 --> 00:39:41,470
you worked for Yan Ke

498
00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:42,950
and lived quite a prosperous life!

499
00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:44,100
How could you still come?

500
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:50,140
Under Your Grace's orders,

501
00:39:50,580 --> 00:39:52,390
I went undercover with Yan Ke.

502
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:56,020
He...

503
00:39:56,020 --> 00:39:57,910
It's the evidence of the violation

504
00:39:58,430 --> 00:40:00,310
of some lords who submitted to Yan Ke.

505
00:40:01,310 --> 00:40:02,220
Please see the truth.

506
00:40:03,140 --> 00:40:05,140
So you weren't loyal to him,

507
00:40:05,620 --> 00:40:06,660
but worked as a spy?

508
00:40:07,500 --> 00:40:08,580
Of course I wasn't loyal.

509
00:40:09,020 --> 00:40:10,020
I endured all these years

510
00:40:11,140 --> 00:40:12,060
just for this day

511
00:40:12,220 --> 00:40:13,060
when Her Grace returned

512
00:40:13,270 --> 00:40:14,110
and set things right.

513
00:40:16,180 --> 00:40:17,430
What a surprise, Yun.

514
00:40:17,580 --> 00:40:18,620
You pretended so perfectly.

515
00:40:18,870 --> 00:40:20,380
For all these years, I misjudged you.

516
00:40:20,580 --> 00:40:22,060
Come on, I'll kowtow to you.

517
00:40:22,390 --> 00:40:23,350
Hey, Leiqi.

518
00:40:23,350 --> 00:40:24,190
It doesn't matter.

519
00:40:26,830 --> 00:40:28,390
We all work for Her Grace.

520
00:40:36,430 --> 00:40:37,310
You may rise.

521
00:40:39,340 --> 00:40:40,180
Thank you.

522
00:40:40,180 --> 00:40:41,020
This is great.

523
00:40:41,350 --> 00:40:42,540
Her Grace is back.

524
00:40:43,100 --> 00:40:44,910
The Void will be back to normal.

525
00:40:45,720 --> 00:40:46,620
So this is how

526
00:40:46,620 --> 00:40:47,620
they have a meeting now.

527
00:40:48,540 --> 00:40:49,380
Interesting.

528
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:54,940
(Liang)

529
00:40:55,310 --> 00:40:56,870
Deliver the intel to Wu Shengliu.

530
00:41:25,710 --> 00:41:31,570
♪Touched memories linger like shadows♪

531
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:37,710
♪Scattered reflections
sink into my heart♪

532
00:41:38,300 --> 00:41:44,310
♪If I could softly call you like this♪

533
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:50,010
♪As gentle as a fleeting embrace♪

534
00:41:52,140 --> 00:41:53,620
It's been five years!

535
00:41:53,620 --> 00:41:54,830
Do you know how worried he is?

536
00:41:54,830 --> 00:41:55,670
You...

537
00:41:57,780 --> 00:42:03,400
♪A lifetime is given
for a name to be remembered♪

538
00:42:03,930 --> 00:42:07,290
♪There are passions and pains♪

539
00:42:07,490 --> 00:42:10,390
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

540
00:42:11,070 --> 00:42:17,300
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

541
00:42:18,610 --> 00:42:21,370
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

542
00:42:21,370 --> 00:42:23,020
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

543
00:42:23,020 --> 00:42:25,850
♪What would come of it?♪

544
00:42:26,260 --> 00:42:27,760
♪I care for no one but you♪

545
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:29,410
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

546
00:42:29,410 --> 00:42:32,590
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

547
00:42:33,110 --> 00:42:35,800
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

548
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:38,550
♪Worth more than any barren land♪

549
00:42:38,790 --> 00:42:41,150
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

550
00:42:41,150 --> 00:42:45,120
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

551
00:42:57,620 --> 00:42:58,460
Simu,

552
00:42:59,500 --> 00:43:00,430
is it really you?

553
00:43:01,470 --> 00:43:02,500
Are you really here?

554
00:43:03,870 --> 00:43:04,710
It's me.

555
00:43:05,040 --> 00:43:09,890
♪Though apart, my thoughts still swirl♪

556
00:43:09,910 --> 00:43:11,390
I summoned you many times.

557
00:43:14,020 --> 00:43:14,860
I know.

558
00:43:18,220 --> 00:43:19,060
But you didn't come.

559
00:43:22,100 --> 00:43:23,270
Now, I've come.

560
00:43:24,600 --> 00:43:29,700
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

561
00:43:29,820 --> 00:43:31,680
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

562
00:43:31,680 --> 00:43:33,290
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

563
00:43:33,290 --> 00:43:36,140
♪What would come of it?♪

564
00:43:36,660 --> 00:43:38,100
♪I care for no one but you♪

565
00:43:38,100 --> 00:43:39,750
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

566
00:43:39,750 --> 00:43:43,000
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

567
00:43:43,420 --> 00:43:46,030
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

568
00:43:47,100 --> 00:43:47,940
I'm all right.

569
00:43:49,080 --> 00:43:51,490
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

570
00:43:51,490 --> 00:43:55,500
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

571
00:44:00,180 --> 00:44:01,270
Never before had I been

572
00:44:01,270 --> 00:44:02,220
that restless.

573
00:44:03,750 --> 00:44:04,870
I couldn't reach you.

574
00:44:06,540 --> 00:44:08,310
And I didn't know what was happening.

575
00:44:11,620 --> 00:44:12,460
Don't worry.

576
00:44:14,700 --> 00:44:16,180
If anything had happened to me,

577
00:44:17,220 --> 00:44:18,350
you would have known.

578
00:44:20,060 --> 00:44:21,750
If I had been annihilated,

579
00:44:22,750 --> 00:44:24,430
the world would have fallen into chaos

580
00:44:25,540 --> 00:44:26,750
and disasters would have raged.

581
00:44:41,440 --> 00:44:46,770
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

582
